### 6. `src/main.jsx`
*(Atenção aqui: ao criar no GitHub, digite `src/main.jsx` para ele criar a pasta `src` automaticamente)*
```react:src/main.jsx
import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'
import App from './App.jsx'
import './index.css'

ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root')).render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>,
)
```eof

